oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Angeline Woods Carter
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Angeline Woods Carter who was born on March 28, 1885 in Arlington, Tennessee and died on May 20, 1956.

Angeline Woods Carter is buried at (Belmont) Hayes Cemetery in Arlington, Tennessee. She was Married to Henry Carter, Jr. (1859-1925) and was the daughter of Redmon (Redman) and Sara Fields Woods. Carter is the great grandmother of the donor.
